*wildfire-2.6.2-r2 (04 Jul 2006)

  04 Jul 2006; Gustavo Felisberto <humpback@gentoo.org>;
  files/conf.d/wildfire, files/init.d/wildfire, -wildfire-2.6.2-r1.ebuild,
  +wildfire-2.6.2-r2.ebuild, +wildfire-3.0.0.ebuild:
